title: Jethro Tull - Songs From The Hippodrome DVD
description:
Jethro Tull live at the Hippodrome in London, England during their "Songs From The Wood" tour, recorded on February 10, 1977:

Skating Away (On The Thin Ice Of The New Day)
Jack-In-The-Green
Thick As A Brick
Songs From The Wood
Velvet Green
Hunting Girl
Aqualung
Guitar Solo
Wind-Up
Lococmotive Breath

Lineup:
Ian Anderson - vocals, flute, acoustic guitar
Martin Barre - electric guitar
John Glascock - bass guitar
John Evan - keyboards
David Palmer - keyboards
Barriemore Barlow - drums and percussion

Enjoy!
